<i>noun</i>: 훈화 [훈ː화], 꾸지람 [꾸지람], 꾸중 [꾸중] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>훈화 [훈ː화]</dt><br>
<dd>instruction; preaching; admonition</dd><br>
<dd>교훈이나 가르침을 주는 말을 함. 또는 그런 말.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of giving another a talk that contains instructive contents or moral lessons; or such a talk.</dd><br>
<dt>꾸지람 [꾸지람]</dt><br>
<dd>scolding; admonition</dd><br>
<dd>윗사람이 아랫사람의 잘못을 꾸짖는 말.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of an elder pointing out a mistake or wrongdoing of a younger person.</dd><br>
<dt>꾸중 [꾸중]</dt><br>
<dd>scolding; admonition</dd><br>
<dd>윗사람이 아랫사람의 잘못을 꾸짖음.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of an elder pointing out a mistake or wrongdoing of a younger person.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>